{"tid":1572353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美軍資料研究] 戰爭中傷亡率達30%即崩潰！就算對面人幾多都好 收佢30%皮就贏！","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:22:13.000Z","uid":123713,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"79804416bbb28dd7f2fcb76ae85471df7d7943dc","tid":1572353,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">網上轉發 </span></span></strong><br />\n崩潰的理論下限是 30%傷亡，傷亡超過此數則無法完成任務。<br />\n精銳部隊或可承受高一些的傷亡率，而弱雞部隊則毫無下限。<br />\n實際戰鬥發生過很多損失超過 30%，但是堅持戰鬥贏下戰鬥的例子。<br />\n<br />\n問題是：作戰參謀敢在作戰計劃中按死傷慘重依然打贏來算嗎？<br />\n不敢的話，那就是按 30%算。<br />\n<br />\n按照美軍文檔 《野戰炮兵行動及火力支援》裏面對炮擊效果的三個定義分別是：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">壓制，中止，殲滅<br />\n壓制：Suppress，短時間內使敵方的作戰能力變得低效，造成至少 3%的傷亡或者物資損失。（使用煙霧彈也算壓制）<br />\n中止：Neutralize，短時間內使敵方失去完成特定任務的能力，造成至少 10%的傷亡或者物資損失。<br />\n殲滅：Destroy，摧毀敵方的作戰意志，造成至少 30%的傷亡或者物資損失，使其永久或者很長時間內無法作戰。<br />\n</span></strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6mAQcN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6mAQcN.jpg&h=d6140f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Field Artillery Operations and Fire Support》<br />\n<br />\n另外，在文檔 AD0875820，《前線空中打擊效果評估：連級部隊傷亡率，被壓制與作戰效能之間的關系》裏面有這麽一份表格，可以看到一個步兵連，士氣全滿，鬥志昂揚投入進攻。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">傷亡率達到 23%的時候，能保持有效戰鬥的人已經不到一半了。<br />\n傷亡率到達 30%的時候，剩余 70%的生還者全部失去了作戰能力，（沒有配合亂打一氣，躲起來消極戰鬥，等等）<br />\n這也是為什麽沖鋒中只損失了一部分兵力，指揮官就會下令退卻，因為剩下來的那些士兵早就無心/無力作戰，要撤退下來整編一下，繼續放在敵人火力下只是白白送死，不會有任何效果。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGR9adu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGR9adu.jpg&h=3b7e3599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《FAST-VAL Relationships Among Casualties, Suppression, and the Performance of Company-Size Units》<br />\n<br />\n有人楞要爭論 XX軍打到最後一個人都沒有崩潰，這種都是特例，另外的 999次正常崩潰，誰會拿出來說。<br />\n補充：步兵連防守的時候，傷亡率與作戰效能的關系，傷亡 50％則剩余士兵也失去戰鬥力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKCTBTm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKCTBTm.jpg&h=266a5b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我還找到另一份 1979年的文檔，AD059384《Casualties as a Measure of The Loss of Combat Effectiveness of an Infantry Battalion 》步兵營的傷亡率與作戰效能<br />\n<br />\n該文研究了二次大戰期間，44個步兵營的傷亡率和 &ldquo;敗退點&rdquo;（Break Point ）<br />\nBreak Point 的定義是：該部隊失去作戰能力，無法完成任務。<br />\n<br />\n分為四個敗退類別<br />\n1 進攻－－短時間的重整－－繼續進攻，9個步兵營<br />\n2 進攻－－轉入防禦，21個步兵營<br />\n3 防禦－－根據命令撤退，13個步兵營<br />\n4 防禦－－完全崩潰，5個步兵營<br />\n<br />\n圖表中展示了前三類步兵營在&ldquo;敗退點&rdquo;的傷亡率分布（包括敗退當天，敗退日倒數3天，以及投入戰鬥至敗退日的累計）<br />\n這是因為作戰持續時間從 2天到22天不等，而較長時間的作戰還可能有兵力補充，如果只算敗退當天的傷亡率則不準確。<br />\n可以看出<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>傷亡率最低的進攻部隊，在累計傷亡 10％左右就失去了進攻能力，最厲害的那個步兵營，也只能承受不到 40%累計傷亡。</strong></span><br />\n而最強悍的防禦部隊，堅持到 70%的累計傷亡才撤退。<br />\n<br />\n關鍵是：敗退當天的部隊傷亡率，統統沒有超過 30%<br />\n可見，短時間內 30%傷亡，這支部隊就立即退出戰鬥了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cj8rWUg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcj8rWUg.jpg&h=9ce63930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較大規模的戰役，也極少累積傷亡率超過 30%而不敗<br />\n下文統計了 92場戰役，時間跨度還挺大，其中包括硫磺島 iwo jima 戰役。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xR8b732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxR8b732.jpg&h=a5b8c5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Historical Data and Lanchester&amp;amp;#39;s Theory of Combat》 part 1 AD480975<br />\n<br />\n結果如下：<br />\n攻擊方取勝 47場，20% 以上傷亡還能取勝的有 9場，30% 以上傷亡勝了 2場，50% 以上傷亡取勝的，一場都沒有。<br />\n防禦方贏了 45場，20% 以上傷亡還能取勝的有 15場，30% 以上傷亡勝了 6場，50% 以上傷亡取勝的，也是一場都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n從這些戰役的統計來看，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">30%的傷亡很高概率敗退</span></strong>，50% 傷亡必定敗退。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3EyBUH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3EyBUH.jpg&h=dd1649fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Historical Data and Lanchester&amp;amp;#39;s Theory of Combat》part 1 <br />\n黑點代表攻擊方取勝，白點代表防禦方取勝。所有戰役的數據點，絕大部分都在坐標（0.3,0.3）的左下方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpLU5N8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpLU5N8.jpg&h=264f6518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，也有人從 平均單日傷亡率 來統計每場戰役。<br />\n《Finding the Important Factors in Battle Outcomes A Statistical Exploration of Data from Major Battles》 a386719 統計了 1600年到 1982年，共計 660場主要戰役。<br />\n美國內戰 0.85 那個數據點是 battle of Front Royal，北軍參戰人數 1063人，南軍 16000+， 毀滅性打擊。。。<br />\n其余戰役的單日傷亡率很少超過 40%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmxHvhu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmxHvhu.jpg&h=7539c8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮戰爭，包括 1951年的上甘嶺戰役。<br />\n投入大量兵力爭奪兩個小山頭，所以上甘嶺戰役的 平均每日傷亡率 很低。<br />\n局部的陣地可能死傷慘重，但對參戰的整支軍隊而言，只不過是損失了一點&ldquo;添油&rdquo;。<br />\n現代戰爭的戰場疏散度很高，所以平均每日傷亡率也大大降低，朝鮮戰爭最高不過 10%。（The DCR values of the attacker and the defender remained below 10% level during the campaign）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNFh3Am.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNFh3Am.jpg&h=28de1ba7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d104c9dcd11c7757576c25a23bcda62409878a15","tid":1572353,"uid":264192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"強帖"},{"pid":"cea6be220fc63cbff5ed64042092392a68133d88","tid":1572353,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb40d518337adb6c94157e933caf6c63df0a9c0d","tid":1572353,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"TLDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e496b74ae92a32258ddf7a539a9f94642cd22ab7","tid":1572353,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"166f0d5d71c193f622b2dd24a14f48a61cdcaec7","tid":1572353,"uid":123713,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb40d518337adb6c94157e933caf6c63df0a9c0d","tid":1572353,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"TLDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"標題都夠做<br />\n橙字係highlight<br />\n成篇都係support緊標題"},{"pid":"afb27f6fd7241f187af5c48d245454041c0d3b02","tid":1572353,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"17e4afd6e69ab9b5900254a569d6de12b9939f2e","tid":1572353,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"06cb3ecfb79993460fbf69643bc5fae4dbe36311","tid":1572353,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"最大問題<br />\n<br />\n是無足夠火力 <br />\n可以對黑警產生極大威脅<br />\n<br />\n一旦小部份人 傷亡<br />\n佢地果種 出來打示威者只係Ot的心態 <br />\n+同狗友圍威喂的心態<br />\n<br />\n就會開始崩潰"},{"pid":"f2b2c6a8e17ce331f9b15639bcde324301d1da2b","tid":1572353,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"問題依家唔係3萬入面嘅30%"},{"pid":"166cda3084439b97d1ca1b1e5a8400e8215fc334","tid":1572353,"uid":304181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd9f634e50b9f0263960fbe3795c04e4c988cdf","tid":1572353,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06cb3ecfb79993460fbf69643bc5fae4dbe36311","tid":1572353,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"最大問題<br />\n<br />\n是無足夠火力 <br />\n可以對黑警產生極大威脅<br />\n<br />\n一旦小部份人 傷亡<br />\n佢地果種 出來打示威者只係Ot的心態 <br />\n+同狗友圍威喂的心態<br />\n<br />\n就會開始崩潰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6994691396f2e9f73e6a186059ac621aa32f7c05","tid":1572353,"uid":261895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5e8895762fb1711f6da1c556f2402c42e4c362","tid":1572353,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2b2c6a8e17ce331f9b15639bcde324301d1da2b","tid":1572353,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"問題依家唔係3萬入面嘅30%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"警隊編制中<br />\n15000係軍裝<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他team 好少落場同文職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再加830個日廿幾架軍車落黎扮換更<br />\n（但又冇車返返去）<br />\n當個到一車30個人啦好未<br />\n20車*30人=600人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目標即係15000+600+老黑既30%"},{"pid":"8771f16122e97414441dca5dd7e9f35782311983","tid":1572353,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"呢個3成預左死人既軍隊<br />\n<br />\n示威者同治安部隊有少冇多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f8863d85dc5caa11c5c6ed74a55a2d6353faf2","tid":1572353,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f117280b6541032b314f8dc7c5a0a19fc17b58fa","tid":1572353,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"7a2cffd89477f1105729ba898f5175cbc5686730","tid":1572353,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5991478284c047c8b579be15f24d53423563362","tid":1572353,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"17c95a0d546875aebacb391e1753a76eab6a009d","tid":1572353,"uid":271690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:06:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f6eda737ada92e861b305d1d9194894b53fad833","tid":1572353,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"即係一個街口KO三四個防暴，佢哋可能喊住咁叫撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2412e8ab0694536b2c3b359128c216b7b1f8876e","tid":1572353,"uid":44019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"軍裝15000,做低4500個我地就嬴?<br />\n示威者200萬人,拉60萬個我地先輸?<br />\n我可唔可以咁理解?"},{"pid":"b78f1f1517ea220d986cb80828f098ed3624c17f","tid":1572353,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2412e8ab0694536b2c3b359128c216b7b1f8876e","tid":1572353,"uid":44019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"軍裝15000,做低4500個我地就嬴?<br />\n示威者200萬人,拉60萬個我地先輸?<br />\n我可唔可以咁理解?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}